Cell["\<\
this code ensures that any upvalues and downvalues of a built-in symbol are \
stored before any changes are made and restored in the case that the symbol \
definition needs to be cleared while resetting the UserLevel. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.74912922198787*^9, 3.749129293383915*^9}, {
